  <name>zeff-boy</name>
  <summary>A Game Boy, Game Boy Color, and NES emulator</summary>
  <metadata_license>MIT</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT OR Apache-2.0</project_license>

  <description>
    <p>
      zeff-boy is a Game Boy, Game Boy Color, and NES emulator written in Rust.
      It features save states, cheats, a libretro core,
      and runs on Windows, macOS, Linux, and the web.
    </p>
